0 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244130/extras/0c7224550247d9a9ba9faa412e296fa3.poster.avif?t=1747128326\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244130/extras/0c7224550247d9a9ba9faa412e296fa3.webm?t=1747128326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244130/extras/0c7224550247d9a9ba9faa412e296fa3.mp4?t=1747128326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244130/extras/a66a60a9e5ede08a03f8315238871824.poster.avif?t=1747128326\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244130/extras/a66a60a9e5ede08a03f8315238871824.webm?t=1747128326\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244130/extras/a66a60a9e5ede08a03f8315238871824.mp4?t=1747128326\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制定可以自由调整的政策。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >阻止市民休息，征收税金才能正常经营城市吧？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过自己制定的政策来预防各种经济和社会问题！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244130/extras/9e5d735fbb468215e2284babd4660b7b.webp?t=1747128326\" width=640 height=50 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2244130/extras/b281d546c8e68809f7bd5f92717110c5.poster.avif?t=1747128326\